    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Order containing seven living species in one family, characterized by unique large keratin scales covering their skin, and being nocturnal animals that use their well-developed sense of smell to find insects.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
